@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

' Define the Client
class Client {
}

' Define the Facade
class Facade {
  + watchMovie()
  + endMovie()
}

' Define the complex subsystem
package "Subsystem Classes" {
  class Amplifier {
    + on()
    + off()
    + setVolume()
  }
  
  class Projector {
    + on()
    + off()
    + wideScreenMode()
  }
  
  class TheaterLights {
    + dim()
    + off()
  }
  
  class StreamingPlayer {
    + on()
    + play()
    + stop()
  }
}

' Relationships
Client -right-> Facade : " Invokes simplified API"
Facade -down-> Amplifier : " Delegates"
Facade -down-> Projector : " Delegates"
Facade -down-> TheaterLights : " Delegates"
Facade -down-> StreamingPlayer : " Delegates"

' Notes for clarity
note top of Facade
  **Facade**
  Provides a unified, high-level interface.
  Shields the Client from subsystem complexity.
end note

note bottom of "Subsystem Classes"
  **Subsystem Classes**
  Implement the actual functionality.
  They have no knowledge of the Facade.
end note

@enduml